'''Jamɛ Lfna''' nɣ s wassaɣ ns iɣzzifn '''Asarag n Jamɛ Lfna''' nɣ '''Abaraz n Jamɛ Lfna''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|Taɛrabt]] : -{ساحة جامع الفنا}-, s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|Tfransist]] : -{Place Jemaa el-Fna}-, s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|Tanglizt]] : -{Jemaa el-Fnaa}- ) iga yan udɣar bahra ittyawssan g tɣrmt n [[Mrrakc]], ittyawssan Jamɛ lfna g ugnsu n [[Lmɣrib]] ula g brra ns. Iga ubaraz n Jamɛ lfna ul n tɣrmt n Mrrakc, ig ula anmuggar n [[Tiɣrmt|tɣrmt]] taqqdimt d Lqqṣbt d [[Lmllaḥ]], ig daɣ anmuggar n [[Afgan|middn]] sg kullu [[Timizar n Umaḍal|timizar]] n [[Amaḍal|umaḍal]], ar sis d ttackan bac ad fjjijn kksn kra f ul nnsn, ar gis ẓṛṛan [[Aɛisawi|iɛisawin]], ar gis ssflidn i [[Tallast|tallasin]] tiqqbuṛin.

[[Amarg|Aẓawan]] illa bdda g Jamɛ lfna zund ukan ntta zund tallast taqqbuṛt d [[Timssḍṣit|timssḍṣitin]] timrrakciyyin, iga Jamɛ lfna yan uḍɣar ismunen tugt n wanawn n [[Taẓuṛi|tẓuṛi]] d [[Amarg|uẓawan]] amɣribi mayad a iwddjan [[Tamaddast n timtta imunn i usgmi, tamassant d tadlsa|MMMSMD]] ad tskr sg Jamɛ lfna yan uḍɣar amaḍlan anfgan.

== Amzruy n ubaraz ==
Abaraz n Jamɛ Lfna ila iẓuṛan imqquṛn g [[Amzruy|umzruy]] n Lmɣrib, acku abaraz ad ttrsn iwttasn ns sg ma ttrsn iwttas n tɣrmt n Mrrakc g uzmz n [[Imrabṭn|imṛabṭn]] g usggas n 1070-1071 [[Ḍaṛt Tlalit|Dat Tlalit]]. Ittyabna ubaraz n Jamɛ Lfna g tizwiri bac a ig [[agdz]] ad gis zznzan middn ar sgis ssaɣn, macc ḍaṛt lbni n timzgida n Lktbiyya s [[tusut]], abaraz n Jamɛ Lfna issnti ar ittgga yan udɣar istawhmman, acku igllidn urrin ar gis skarn yan usfsr nɣ yan unmuggar n tɣrmt n [[Mrrakc]], anmuggar n middn d tasrdist<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref>; akud nna ira ukllid a iffɣ s kra n imnɣi nɣ ig d yaɣɣul ar iskar anmuggar g ubaraz n Jamɛ Lfna.

